# Lottie Animations Directory

Place your Lottie JSON animation files here.

## Usage

```tsx
import { LottieAnimation } from "@/components/animation";

// Basic usage
<LottieAnimation animationPath="my-animation.json" />

// Play on hover
<LottieAnimation animationPath="icon.json" playOnHover loop={false} />

// Play when scrolled into view
<LottieAnimation animationPath="scroll-reveal.json" playOnView />
```

## File Format

- Export animations from After Effects using the Bodymovin plugin
- Use JSON format (not dotLottie)
- Keep file sizes reasonable (optimize assets)
